{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "09", "m": "03", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "20", "M": "20", "S": "29"}}, "news": [{"title": "Jewar airport to be inaugurated soon: Civil aviation minister", "para": "Jewar airport in Uttar Pradesh has received its aerodrome licence and will begin operations shortly. The Civil Aviation Minister announced this development in the Rajya Sabha. The government is committed to expanding India's airport network, with plans for new airports and upgrades across the country. This initiative aims to boost regional connectivity and accommodate growing air travel demand.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/infrastructure/jewar-airport-to-be-inaugurated-soon-civil-aviation-minister/129338353?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-40904/129338353.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "infrastructure"}, {"title": "Jaipur: About 2,000 Sanganer residents march to protect homes", "para": "Nearly 2,000 residents from 87 Sanganer colonies protested a housing board land acquisition, fearing for their homes. Families have lived in these colonies for years, built houses with bank loans, and developed civic facilities. Residents issued a 15-day ultimatum to the state government for a resolution, threatening intensified agitation if their concerns are not addressed.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/residential/sanganer-residents-march-for-home-security-amid-land-acquisition-concerns/129340630?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-112422/129340630.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "residential"}, {"title": "Raymond Realty to jointly develop Mumbai project; County Group unveils \u20b91,200 crore project in Noida", "para": "Raymond Realty is developing a new residential project in Kandivali, Mumbai. This project has a gross development value of \u20b93,000 crore. Meanwhile, County Group has launched Clove County, a luxury residential project in Noida. This project features 226 apartments with prices ranging from \u20b910 crore to \u20b918 crore.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/raymond-realty-to-jointly-develop-mumbai-project-county-group-unveils-1200-crore-project-in-noida/129335603?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-77930/129335603.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}]}